                            <comment id="14631468" author="granthenke" created="Fri, 17 Jul 2015 15:27:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Created reviewboard &lt;a href=&quot;https://reviews.apache.org/r/36570/diff/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://reviews.apache.org/r/36570/diff/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 against branch origin/trunk&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14631474" author="granthenke" created="Fri, 17 Jul 2015 15:30:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Checks all topic creation including auto-create&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fails with InvalidTopicException when topics collide (periods and underscores in the same position)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Warns when a topic with a period or underscore is created via kafka-topics.sh&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14631525" author="granthenke" created="Fri, 17 Jul 2015 16:17:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Updated reviewboard &lt;a href=&quot;https://reviews.apache.org/r/36570/diff/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://reviews.apache.org/r/36570/diff/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
